    "description": "<strong><i>Gnomes vs Knights: A Whimsical Clash</i></strong><br><br>Dive into the enchanted forest where gnomes and knights clash in a chaotic, laugh-out-loud PvP showdown! With <strong>support for 2 to 32 players</strong>, you can battle it out with friends or foes in this fast-paced, action-packed game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features (or &quot;Ways to Ruin a Perfectly Good Day&quot;):</h2><br><strong>Gnomes: The Sneaky Saboteurs</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Wield the Pink Butterfly Net: It’s quirky, it’s fun, and it’s surprisingly effective.<br></li><li>Vanish at Will: Turn invisible and outsmart those clueless knights with the press of a button.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105980/extras/ccf2d65e00ce3091c27140b2a246b57f.poster.avif?t=1725649030\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105980/extras/ccf2d65e00ce3091c27140b2a246b57f.webm?t=1725649030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105980/extras/ccf2d65e00ce3091c27140b2a246b57f.mp4?t=1725649030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Knights: The Clumsy Crusaders</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Swing Your Sword: Three hits take down a gnome, but watch your stamina!<br></li><li>Run Like the Wind: Sprint with Shift—just don’t run out of breath mid-chase.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105980/extras/e1127bee39011b39db51b24fb9bcd832.poster.avif?t=1725649030\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105980/extras/e1127bee39011b39db51b24fb9bcd832.webm?t=1725649030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105980/extras/e1127bee39011b39db51b24fb9bcd832.mp4?t=1725649030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Bonus Chaos: Beware the chickens!</strong><br>Touch one, and you’re frozen in place while it flaps away in a flurry of feathers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105980/extras/5c586b390d372311bbc5467b9e988d44.poster.avif?t=1725649030\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105980/extras/5c586b390d372311bbc5467b9e988d44.webm?t=1725649030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105980/extras/5c586b390d372311bbc5467b9e988d44.mp4?t=1725649030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Can you lead your team to victory in this whimsical clash? Grab your net or sword, and let the mayhem begin!",
